description.0: The origin of Zabu, loyal companion to Ka-Zar!
description.1: When Daredevil and Urich continue to dig on the Cherryh story, Elektra is dispatched to put a stop to their muckraking.
description.2: A cursed spirit begins purging Bruce Banner of the Gamma rays that hold him prisoner in his own body. Will the price of freedom outweigh the price of morality?
description.3: Stark International's construction is complete. Tony acquires all assets from Cord Conglomerate much to his delight.
description.5: The Bi-Beast escapes! But Thor and Iron Man are in fast pursuit...deep in the Florida Everglades!
description.6: Wolverine's been accused...of Hulk's murder! What conflict led to Wolverine piercing Hulk's gamma-irradiated hide? And will the X-Men bail Logan out of this sticky situation? In the world of What Ifs?, anything's possible!
description.7: Ben's Aunt Petunia pays the FF a visit- and is in need of some investigative help with mysterious deaths in her town! Meanwhile, a war is raging in the Inhuman city of Attilan.
description.8: The Starjammers arrive in time to deal with an interplanetary menace.
description.17: She-Hulk decides to go directly after Shade, and Sheriff Morris Walters comes to a realization!
description.18: Gargoyle's home has been overrun by a mysterious demonic entity! Who or what is Null the Living Darkness, and how will it change Isaac Christians' life forever?
description.20: Foggy thinks Matt Murdock could use some bodyguards, so he enlists the help of the only people capable of doing the job: the Heroes For Hire. Featuring everyone's favorite tag-team supreme Iron Fist and Power Man!
description.21: Glorian turns a town of people against Hulk by disguising its citizens as Hulk's greatest enemies!
description.22: Iron Man faces a dangerous new threat in a suited villain calling himself the Unicorn. But this Unicorn is far from fantasy-land lore. Also featuring Titanium Man!
description.23: Just when Don Blake is back in the medical game...things take a turn for the worse! Can Thor defend the ship he's working on from the menacing Bi-Beast?
description.24: Frankie Raye discovers her true powers! All is revealed with her origin story. Could this mean the Fantastic Four are about to become the Fantastic Five?
description.25: Presenting, Kitty's Fairy Tale.  Featuring the evil Dark Phoenix, the wizard Xavier, dragons, magic, and much more!
description.28: Hela and her new Hell-Lord allies create the Nexus of the Netherworlds, summoning forth a being of primal destruction: the Demogorge!
description.30: Jeff Mace, an alternate Captain America, has a conversation with Elder of the Universe, the Contemplator. Facing his own mortality and an end to his costumed days, Mace and Steve Rogers take on the past to face a costly future.
description.33: The battle against Terrax continues! Can Dazzler defeat this hand of Galactus and finally return home?
description.34: The Vulture has returned and he's deadlier than ever! A former electrical engineer, Adrian Toomes has smarts that match Peter Parker's. How will Spider-Man outwit his foe this time? A battle of brains, technology, and super strength!
description.35: A special Silver Surfer-centric issue! What happens when Silver Surfer discovers the discarded wand of Molecule Man? And why is Tigra in grave danger because of this discovery?
description.36: When Captain America is abducted, it's up to Spider-Man and Nick Fury to save him! But when the super villain is revealed to be none other than the Sultan, things take an ugly turn for the worse. Don't miss this thrilling issue when Spider-Man teams up with S.H.I.E.L.D.!
description.40: Leia's choice for a new Rebel base on the forest planet known as Arbra may be a deadly decision!
description.41: While on the run, the rebels take shelter in a convent. But not everything is how it appears in this house of worship...
description.45: Ka-Zar, Shanna, and Dherk encounter more mythic evils including the three-headed dog Cerberus!
description.46: Nighthawk, still reeling from the Defenders' last battle, visits an old flame to try and get back on his feet - only to run into even MORE trouble! What dark secrets does Mindy Williams hide?
description.48: Spider-Man leaps in to stop a burglar - but that might be more than he bargained for when the burglar is a powered-up MOONSTONE!
description.49: She-Hulk at war! Torque is out to assassinate Jennifer Walters!
description.50: Can Stick help restore Daredevil's radar sense? And what does the Kingpin make of the assassin Elektra?
description.51: Everything's gone bananas in the New Mexico desert! All humans in the area have turned into apes- including Betty and Rick!
description.52: The Living Laser has pledged allegiance to Heaven's Hand, and Iron Man must stop him. Bethany confronts Tony about their relationship, and ultimately leaves to care for her still-alive husband, Alex.
description.54: Donald Blake's clinic has closed! Will the good doctor find his purpose again? Meanwhile, Moondragon and Drax the Destroyer discover their similar feelings towards life.
description.55: Remember the original Spider-Man clone saga? Now picture the events entirely inverted! Peter Parker's clone survives, and attempts to rebuild a life from the memories of a stranger. Will the world embrace two Spider-Men?
description.56: The Richard's family encounters Spinerette, an alien who's been robbing New York City jewelry stores! Meanwhile, Johnny is hit with a sudden shock at the apartment of Frankie Raye!
description.57: When the White Queen takes over Storm's mind, will Ororo be lost forever?
description.61: Dormammu uses Baron Mordo as his pawn, before the Ancient One's fallen disciple can carry out his vengeance on Strange!
description.62: Galactus is after Dazzler's power! Our titular hero fights a cosmic battle against the Devourer of Worlds… but he isn't alone.
description.63: Dherk acclimates to his new robotic form with help from some friends. A new corridor reveals tiny mythical animals!
description.68: It's a true Animal House, as Red Ghost and his Super-Apes crash a college party at ESU! Good thing Peter Parker got an invite. Spider-Man takes down Red Ghost in the ESU library, and is aided by shy graduate student Roger Hochberg!
description.69: The Avengers head to the deserts of New Mexico to investigate an unprovoked attack on Warren Worthington, and his girlfriend Candy Southern. Yellowjacket attempts to reconcile with Jan, but she has already motioned for divorce. Guest-starring Ghost Rider!
description.70: Captain America and Falcon must team up against a horde of Nazi, to save the X-Men, the world's strangest super heroes!
description.74: On the planet Shiva IV, the Rebels fight another battle against the Empire that they may not all escape from.
description.75: The fallout from the Defenders' duel with the Devil starts here! The shock of losing one of their own splinters the team, and it may never recover! Which of the Defenders will stay, and which will leave for good?
description.76: The Fantastic Four link their common nightmares back to the Puppet Master, who is employed by their greatest nemesis- Doctor Doom!
description.77: BEETLEMANIA! The Beetle is out for revenge against Spider-Man, and it quickly turns into an all-out brawl - and you won't BELIEVE who lands the K.O. punch!
description.78: BAD VIBES! She-Hulk is attacked by Radius, a super-villain who uses the power of energy vortexes.
description.79: This is the final showdown: Elektra versus Kiringi! Plus, Daredevil and Elektra track down Matt's old sensei, the man called Stick.
description.80: Ghost Rider goes international and throws down with some oil monsters!
description.81: Rick Jones and the Rangers team up to save a hypnotized Hulk!
description.82: Iron Man goes on a rescue mission to recover Bethany Cabe. After reconnoitering information in East Germany, Tony and Rhodey team-up to find Bethany's exact locale at the Heaven's Hand base.
description.83: Sif is the deciding vote in Thor's hearing that will determine his privileges to go to and from Earth. Will Thor's lover choose with her head...or her heart?
description.84: Kitty's parents have her removed from Xavier's school. But they end up enrolling her in an academy run by Emma Frost, the White Queen of the Hellfire Club.
description.88: Where in the world is Alison Blaire? Project Pegasus has been testing Dazzler's powers for a while now. What will she do to get back to her everyday life?
description.89: Leia crashes on the planet Shiva IV, but what she finds is more Imperials!
description.93: With their discovery of Pangea, Ka-Zar and Shanna encounter one ancient threat after another. Now, a labyrinthine cave of advanced tech offers an even greater challenge.
description.96: Spider-Man faces humiliating defeat at the hands of Speed Demon. And to make matters worse, Spidey's snafu makes front page news! Determined to catch Speed Demon in his web, Spider-Man sets some sticky traps in high end retailers. Plus, Speed Demon's unusual origin!
description.97: Yellowjacket continues to cause concern for his teammates after several bouts of reckless behavior in battle. But who will truly take the blunt of Hank Pym's rage? Will it be the woman he loves more than life itself? A shocking issue that reveals the dark side to one of Earth's Mightiest Heroes!
description.98: Cap's battle with Ameridriod continues! During his struggle with the android, it is revealed that one of Cap's most villainous foes is behind it all. It's the return of the Red Skull!
description.99: The Defenders battle Satan and his fellow Hell-Lords, but even that showdown pales before the ultimate hellish duel: Daimon vs. Satan, son vs. father!

9.text: The mark of the Molten Man!

10.text: The Thing guest-stars! Ben Grimm and Moon Knight combine forces to complete a little boy’s vendetta. Plus, Moon Knight is hired to steal the head of Medusa! Will the merc get caught in her stony gaze?

11.text: Power Man, Iron Fist, Misty Knight, and Colleen Wing build a team to capture the Slasher, who has been terrorizing the city with his crime streaks.

12.text: Featuring the deadly return of Zaran the Weapons Master!

15.text: For his interference with an alien culture, Nebulon is exiled on Earth. But when the would-be world conqueror befriends Thor of the Avengers, can the super powerhouse find solidarity amongst the Earth’s heroes?

17.text: She-Hulk decides to go directly after Shade, and Sheriff Morris Walters comes to a realization!

18.text: Gargoyle's home has been overrun by a mysterious demonic entity! Who or what is Null the Living Darkness, and how will it change Isaac Christians' life forever?

19.text: Storm, under the possession of Dracula! See what happens when the X-Woman loses control over her body and mind. Will young Shadowcat be able to save her mentor? Witness Kitty Pryde at her plucky best as she rouses the X-Men to save Storm from the grip of Dracula!

26.text: Beware the glittering gun of Gold Bug!

29.text: A green plague has befallen New York City! And everyone is blaming the Hulk! Can the Hulk stop the Leader, the true villain behind the poisoning of the city?

31.text: While Giant-Man fights radiation poisoning, the Thing travels to Canada to get the help of Walt Langkowski.

37.text: When Shang-Chi accepts a job as a bodyguard, he wonders if the person he's protecting is actually the danger himself.

42.text: Moon Knight- assassin? Marc Spector’s morality becomes even more blurry when Xenos and his army of rats enter the fray!

43.text: Power Man and Iron Fist work as the body guards to Elyena, the injured ballerina who is on the hunt from Russian dancing-duo Ninotchka and Boris!

46.text: Nighthawk, still reeling from the Defenders' last battle, visits an old flame to try and get back on his feet - only to run into even MORE trouble! What dark secrets does Mindy Williams hide?

48.text: Spider-Man leaps in to stop a burglar - but that might be more than he bargained for when the burglar is a powered-up MOONSTONE!

49.text: She-Hulk at war! Torque is out to assassinate Jennifer Walters!

64.text: After fasting, Shang-Chi is weakened before his showdown with Sata.

71.text: Moon Knight runs afoul of a criminal mastermind…and his mother! Scarlet Fasinera will stop at nothing to protect her son. Will Moon Knight be able to deliver justice before this mother with a mission beats him to the punch?

72.text: Iron Fist, Colleen, and Misty fight off Warhawk!

73.text: Spider-Man! Firestar! Iceman! The Amazing Friends face the wrath of Green Goblin in one standout issue!

75.text: The fallout from the Defenders' duel with the Devil starts here! The shock of losing one of their own splinters the team, and it may never recover! Which of the Defenders will stay, and which will leave for good?

77.text: BEETLEMANIA! The Beetle is out for revenge against Spider-Man, and it quickly turns into an all-out brawl - and you won't BELIEVE who lands the K.O. punch!

78.text: BAD VIBES! She-Hulk is attacked by Radius, a super-villain who uses the power of energy vortexes.

80.text: Ghost Rider goes international and throws down with some oil monsters!

90.text: Leiko and Shang-Chi try to break into the fortress of Velcro.

94.text: Co-starring Daredevil! Two shadowy vigilantes, hot on the trail of The Jester. But why? Witness Moon Knight and Daredevil in their very first team-up!

95.text: Crash landing in K’un-Lun, Iron Fist finds himself in the middle of Master Khan’s plans for Iron Fist to be sacrificed!

99.text: The Defenders battle Satan and his fellow Hell-Lords, but even that showdown pales before the ultimate hellish duel: Daimon vs. Satan, son vs. father!
